                                            [close "https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLDialogElement/close_event"]))))

                    (,, (comment "https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement"
                                 (,, (these [beforeinput "https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/beforeinput_event"]
